# Hourbour — Design System
LONG-TERM. Load for any UI, visual, or component work on Hourbour.
⚠️ These rules OVERRIDE any design content in agent MEMORY.md files for Hourbour work.
Cross-venture shared patterns → docs/memory/design.md

---

## Aesthetic Direction
Clean fintech. Trustworthy blue. Data-forward. No clutter.
Professional, modern palette — can support light or dark mode
Data visualisations are first-class UI — charts, progress bars, numbers need breathing room
App UI screenshots are valid creative assets
Clean edges, clear hierarchy, no decorative noise

