## Component Rules
Data tables: always show column units in header, not in each cell
Charts: label axes, include a zero-line where relevant
KPI cards: value large + prominent, delta below in green/red
Buttons: filled primary (blue), outlined secondary
No decorative elements — every pixel earns its place

